    <p>The major features of this application are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>User can create his account with minimum personal information.</li>
      <li>User can draw a sketch choosing different thikness of brush and choosing one of several colors available in the current version</li>
      <li>
        User can upload an image via link from internet or from his computer.</li>
        <li>User can view his image album, look at any image closer and edit it in the editor, then save it and overwrite it</li>
      </ul>
      <br />
      <h4>Languages and technologies I've used</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Back-end: Ruby on Rails 4.0</li>
        <li>Non relational database MongoDB and Mongoid ORM to control it. Uploaded images are stored on Amazon S3 Web Services</li>
        <li>The logic of the actual editor is written in JavaScript with elemnts of jQuery and AJAX thecnics</li>
      </ul>
